item.title: CVE-2018-8575|2024-08-05T07:02:25.601Z -- microsoft -- microsoft%20project
item.description: A remote code execution vulnerability exists in Microsoft Project software when it fails to properly handle objects in memory, aka "Microsoft Project Remote Code Execution Vulnerability." This affects Microsoft Project, Office 365 ProPlus, Microsoft Project Server.
